INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('My Tiny Land', 3508, 'An ultra-quiet and super stress-relieving fruit and vegetable matching game with hundreds of types of fruits waiting for you to collect.You can drag identical fruits into a basket, and eliminating them requires only a match of three. To win, you need to eliminate all the fruits and vegetables within the specified time limit. The game boasts simple controls and engaging game play.', 'Once the game begins drag the fruits or vegetables in the baskets to form groups of three which will then be eliminated To win the game and advance to the next level you must eliminate all the fruits or vegetables in all the baskets', 'English'),
('Slice Sprunki Clicker', 3509, 'Slice Sprunki Clicker is a fast-paced slicing survival game. Slash Sprunki characters as they fly across the screen. Avoid bombs and time your cuts for maximum points. The challenge gets harder with each wave, testing your reflexes. Smooth animations and dynamic effects make every slice satisfying. Play endless mode and see how long you can survive. Compete for high scores and master precision cutting. Perfect for fans of arcade and reaction-based games. Jump into the slicing madness and chop Sprunki to pieces!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Mustard All Phases', 3510, 'Sprunki Mustard All Phases is an action-packed platformer that takes you on a wild ride through a vibrant, fast-paced world filled with quirky challenges and unique mechanics. Guide Sprunki, a fearless mustard-themed hero, through various dynamic phases, dodging obstacles, battling enemies, and unlocking powerful upgrades. With its colorful graphics, smooth controls, and engaging gameplay, this game delivers a thrilling experience for casual and hardcore gamers alike!', 'How to Play Move ndash Use arrow keys or swipe controls to navigate through levels Jump amp Double Jump ndash Tap the jump button to leap over obstacles and avoid dangers Attack ndash Use the action button to eliminate enemies in your way', 'English'),
('Dropping Gems', 3511, 'Race against time in this dazzling arcade challenge where quick reflexes meet strategic gem collecting! Guide your mystical basket through a starlit void, snatching colorful gems as they cascade from above. But beware - deadly bombs threaten to end your crystal-catching spree! Power up with magical shields, time-warping clocks, and score multipliers to become the ultimate gem master. How many precious stones can you gather before time runs out? Test your skills in this addictively simple yet thrilling cosmic collection adventure!', 'On Mobile - Swipe On Desktop - Click and drag Basket or use left and right keys', 'English'),
('NG: Flow Lines', 3512, 'Flow Lines is an engaging and straightforward puzzle game where the main objective is to connect dots of the same color through a continuous path on a grid.', 'To play Flow Lines tap on a colored dot and drag your finger across the screen to create a path connecting it to another dot of the same color Ensure that the lines are continuous and do not overlap The goal is to fill every square on the grid without', 'English'),
('Cube Tower Stack 3D', 3513, 'In this causal game we are providing 9 New characters and you can play the game by collecting coins while moving character building stacks, super fun entertainment game. When you reaching the end of the level you do come across with 7 number of steps to double, multiple your coins. c', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Chase Zombie', 3514, 'In Zombie Chase, players navigate a chaotic world filled with the undead, using every ounce of strategic prowess to outlast the apocalypse. This is not a typical racing game, youll need to manage resources and make smart decisions to survive the relentless zombie hordes. Your brain isnt just a desirable snack for zombies in this game - its your greatest weapon!', 'Using your mouse or touchscreen controls steer your character through the grid-based game world avoiding zombies and collecting resources as you go You can also set traps for zombies but be careful not to get cornered yourself Progress in the game re', 'English'),
('Money Chaser   Parkour Game', 3515, 'Chasing/Running endlessly for collecting coins(Money). Try to avoid traps &amp;amp; *kick out all the enemy/competitors on your way. *You can kick out enemy infront of you with slide skill* After you have enough money, you can challenge the Boss fight. The amount of coins(Money Bullets) is the only weapon to defeat Boss, the more the better. Remember, no money no life...just keep running :)', 'For Keyboard Space Key rarr Jump A Key rarr Slide or Shoot In Boss Battle For Touch Screen Mobile Tap Right Part of Screen rarr Jump Tap Left Part of Screen rarr Slide or Shoot In Boss Battle', 'English'),
('NG: The Word Search', 3516, 'The Word Search is a riveting game that pits your vocabulary knowledge against a complex puzzle of words and jumbled letters. Dive into the depths of thorny English crosswords, unleashing your linguistic prowess to discover hidden words. This game pushes the boundaries of conventional word-finding games, proving to be a unique and challenging endeavor for even the most seasoned puzzle enthusiasts.', 'A word list is given on one side while a chaotic grid of scrambled letters takes up the rest of the screen Your mission is to find and highlight all the listed words within that grid Words can be oriented up down diagonally and even backwards To hi', 'English'),
('OIIA OIIA CAT Drift Master', 3517, 'OIIA OIIA CAT Drift Master is a fun and fast-paced drifting game where players control a car with OIIA OIIA Cat perched adorably on top. The objective is simple but challenging: drift your way around each level and hit all the snow piles while avoiding barriers. With responsive controls and a focus on timing and precision, players must master their drifting skills to clear each stage and become the ultimate Drift Master. In this game, players can purchase different cars, each offering a unique driving experience. There&amp;rsquo;s no customization&amp;mdash;just pick your favorite car and hit the track! The key to success lies in mastering how to drift left and', 'left and right arrow - turn left right', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Matrix Man', 3518, 'MATRIX MAN: OVERRIDE Escape the System, Become the Glitch! The world is a lie, a digital prison controlled by weak NPCs &amp;zwj;. You are built different&amp;mdash;Matrix Man&amp;mdash;a high-value shooter with insane reflexes, bullet-time dodges &amp;zwj;, and next-level hacking skills. RUN the system or RULE it. Headshots only&amp;mdash;no weak moves. Unlock forbidden cyber-weapons. Break free, take over, and OWN the game. Most will stay plugged in. Only legends will OVERRIDE. Are you ready?', 'Move Arrow keys WASD Aim Mouse Jump Space J Fire Left Mouse Button Z Throw Disruptor Right Mouse Button X Slow-Mo Focus Left Shift C Cycle Weapons Mouse Wheel Q E Enter Vehicle E Enter Pause Esc P Mute Audio M Change View V', 'English'),
('Huggy Coloring', 3519, 'Explore the creepy and creative world of Huggy Coloring! Bring the iconic Huggy character to life with vibrant colors and unique art tools. Perfect for fans of Poppy Playtime and horror-themed games, this game combines relaxation with a spooky twist. Unleash your inner artist and create your own Huggy masterpiece today!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Melania Hat Antistress Game', 3520, 'Melania Hat Antistress Game is a charming and free online game designed especially for kids, offering a fun and relaxing experience. In this lighthearted game, you can interact with our lovely Melania in various playful ways, experimenting with different hats and amusing animations. With simple controls and an engaging design, its perfect for players of all ages looking to unwind and enjoy stress-free entertainment. Dive into the fun, explore creative possibilities, and let your imagination run wild. Play Melania Hat Antistress Game now and enjoy endless moments of joy!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Shelf Shift Match', 3521, 'Test your strategy and speed in Shelf Shift Match! Shift items on the shelves to create perfect matches of three, clearing the way to reveal hidden shadowed items. But beware&amp;mdash;unwise moves can block your shelves, leaving no space to shift and leading to game over! If youre stuck, use the shuffle button to mix things up and find new matches.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Fruit Party Clicker', 3522, 'Tired of the same old games? Get ready for the ultimate fruit-tapping challenge! It starts simple, just you and a red apple. Tap as fast as you can, rack up coins, and break your own high score. But thats just the beginning. With every tap, you earn coins that let you unlock a whole collection of fruits, bananas, strawberries, watermelons, and more! Each fruit comes with its own unique look, and you can even upgrade their effects to make tapping even more exciting. The more you play, the crazier the challenge gets. Why You&amp;rsquo;ll Love This Game: Endless Tapping Fun:- Easy to play, impossible to put down. Just tap and watch the points stack up!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pull The Pins', 3523, 'Pull the Pins is a strategic puzzle game where you must carefully pull pins in the correct order to rescue a young boy and make him reach his brother. Each decision matters, as a wrong move could lead to failure. Plan your actions wisely and use problem-solving skills to ensure a successful rescue.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Five Nights at Spikes', 3524, 'Night. You are struggling to sleep because there is clearly something wrong in this house... After a morning inspection, you found strange-looking plush toys (which someone has carefully left here!), and something about them terrifies you... Youve fallen asleep and suddenly woke up to the sound of the clock striking 12. And then the real nightmare began. The house is filled with unknown, evil sounds; the footsteps of both small, neat paws and big, fat plush paws can be heard everywhere... Its Spike and his friends who have begun hunting for you! All you have is a phone with cameras, a flashlight, and a few tennis balls! Good luck!', 'On PC Holding or pressing X Activates various functions Holding or pressing Z Turns on the flashlight Look around Use the mouse by aiming the pointer at the sides of the screen All other controls are mapped to UI buttons', 'English'),
('Modern Sudoku', 3525, 'Modern Sudoku offers a fresh twist on the classic puzzle game with a sleek design and 20 unique boxes instead of the traditional 9x9 grid. Enjoy a vibrant gradient background and modern input fields as you complete the puzzle by filling in the missing numbers. This fast-paced, visually engaging game encourages players to test their logic and problem-solving skills. Featuring a win screen for successful completion and a draw screen for retrying, Modern Sudoku keeps you hooked with its challenging gameplay. Perfect for both casual players and Sudoku enthusiasts, Modern Sudoku delivers a modernized, fun puzzle experience for all. Play Now!', 'Click or tap on any empty box to select it Enter a number between 1 and 9 by typing on the keyboard or selecting it from the on-screen keypad if available Once all the boxes are filled the game will automatically check if the puzzle is correct', 'English'),
('Dino Robot Fighting War', 3526, 'Unleash the clash of giants in Dino Robot Fighting War. In this action game, you can build,customize and fight against many dinosaur robots. Choose from many dino warriors like T-Rex,Triceratops, or Stegosaurus.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Super Mario Clicker', 3527, 'Super Mario Clicker is a fun, clicker, idle game where you help Mario and Friends on an Adventure of infinite Coins. Click to earn coins and unlock all Mario friends as Luigi, Peach, Toad, Yoshi and Bowser. With vibrant visuals, fast-paced challenges, and endless opportunities to push your limits, this quirky game will keep you coming back for more sky-high clicking. Get your fingers ready for a non-stop clickable challenge.', 'Easy to understand Nice and addictive gameplay Rhythm-based clicker gameplay Many characters to unlock Cute Graphics Relaxing gameplay Use the Touch or mouse to click', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Food Castle Tower Defense', 3528, 'Food Castle - Tower Defense is a deliciously fun battle where your culinary skills meet strategic defense. Protect your food kingdom from many tableware enemies by building a strong defensive tower. In this tower defense game, you should protect your castle from enemies.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('New Years Cube in 3D', 3529, 'This game is in the style of 2048, but now in 3D! Disassemble a figure consisting of blocks and cubes! To complete a level, you need to disassemble it all, but do not rush! In the game, you will have a limited number of moves, and if they run out, you will have to complete the level again! The game perfectly trains intelligence and intuition! This game is also great for children, pleasant music and measured gameplay will give your child a good mood! Blue, unobtrusive background will immerse you in the spring and summer atmosphere! You can also compete for the title of the best player on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to disassemble the cubes but over time there will be more and more of them Once you have disassembled all the cubes the next level will begin', 'English'),
('Assassin Knight', 3530, 'Step into the thrilling world of Hunter Knight a fast-paced online game for stealthy and strategic players that takes you on a wild adventure as a hunter with a deadly knife. With multiple enemies to kill, challenging missions to complete and rewards to collect, this game will test your skills and keep you on the edge of your seat.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Christmas Dentist Doctor', 3531, 'Christmas Dentist Doctor is an educational dentist game for kids. Christmas is coming soon. Have you ever thought about what you should do if Santa has a dental disease? Now you can see a dentist for Santa and his moose. You can become a veterinarian and cure Santas assistant.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Animal Impossible Track Rush', 3532, 'Ready for an exciting animal parkour arcade challenge? In the Animal Impossible Track Rush, you&amp;rsquo;ll become a brave animal running across a track. Right now race with your animal and show impossible tracks runner stunts in bouncing recreation in the toughest impossible animal rush 3d challenge.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fill One Line', 3533, 'Dive into the world of fascinating logic and test your mind in an exciting puzzle! Your task is to draw a line across the entire playing field, filling it completely, but keep in mind: there will be obstacles on the way that you need to bypass. The game offers many levels, from simple to incredibly difficult, allowing each player to choose a suitable challenge. Each level is unique: thoughtful routes, various field shapes and unexpectedly located barriers will force you to look for non-standard solutions.', 'Mouse click or Playing our puzzle is simple and fun Your goal is to fill the entire playing field with one continuous line avoiding obstacles How to play Start from the chosen starting point Draw a line connecting the cells of the field to fill them', 'English'),
('Valentines Hidden Alphawords', 3534, 'Experience the joy of love with Valentines Hidden Alphawords, the latest Valentines Day game from lofgames.com. Search for hidden letters in beautiful images, and once you find them all, youll reveal a lovely caption for the picture! With 30 exciting levels to challenge you, race against time and use hints when needed. Enjoy the fun and celebrate love in a whole new way!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Flappy Stickman', 3535, 'Flappy Stickman is a thrilling arcade challenge where you guide a stickman through a series of obstacles. Tap to keep him in the air and avoid crashing. Test your reflexes with fast-paced gameplay that gets harder over time. Compete for high scores and challenge your friends. Enjoy a minimalist design with smooth animations and addictive mechanics. Perfect for casual gamers looking for quick fun. Simple to play but hard to master. Endless gameplay ensures hours of entertainment. Play online anytime and improve your tapping skills. Can you achieve the highest score?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Lone Sniper', 3536, 'You only have 50 seconds to destroy all the enemies. Act very quickly, take a shot and hide behind cover so as not to come under return fire.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hole Attack   Master Collector', 3537, 'This Christmas, the black hole is on a mission &amp;ndash; to devour all the festive delights! Swipe to control its every move, attack with powerful bullets, and challenge your skills in this yuletide adventure.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('BanJia', 3538, 'Casual Moving Game,Includes house decoration!A level-breaking game with a store system that can be used to purchase new skins.Thanks for playing!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Glass Ball Puzzle', 3539, 'In the captivating Glass Ball Puzzle game, your keen eye for color is put to the test. Navigate through this vibrant, color-based puzzle which takes an innovative twist on traditional sorting games. With each level, youll have to segregate intricately mixed balls of different hues and smartly maneuver them into corresponding cups. This game is a test of logic, patience, and precision.', 'To win in this challenging game you rsquo ll need a mouse or touchscreen Simply click or tap on a glass ball to pick it up and release it over a cup of the same color The progression in the game is defined by levels each new level will offer greater c', 'English'),
('Food Slicer  Food Cutting Game', 3540, 'Looking for a new veggie slice &amp;amp; fruit slice game? Love the thrill of chop-chop and slice it challenges? Well, you are sure to adore the new Food Slicer game. Show great chef skills and Whether you need to cut bread, cut vegetables, cut fruits, showcase great reaction, cutting precision, and avoid hitting the wood deck! Can you complete all chopping food levels? Start your quest to slice perfect slices NOW!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tank Arena Steel Battle', 3541, 'Welcome to Tank Arena Steel Battle. Want to drive your tank and enter the heart of the battle arena? This action tank shooting game will test your skills, strategy, and quick reflexes. This game offers nervous challenges. Control a cool tank and fight enemies in the arena.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ratomilton at Squid Game Backrooms', 3542, 'Step into the mysterious and terrifying world of the backrooms, where reality bends, and danger lurks around every corner. In Ratomilton in Squid Game Backrooms, you take on the role of Rato Milton, a cheerful, ever-dancing mouse who finds himself trapped in this eerie maze. But escaping won&amp;rsquo;t be easy&amp;mdash;Squid Game soldiers are patrolling the area, and they won&amp;rsquo;t hesitate to catch anyone who tries to flee. Your mission is simple but challenging: navigate through the endless, dimly lit corridors of the backrooms, collect all the required items, and find the escape door before the soldiers catch you. With every step you take, the tension rises. T', 'WASD - move', 'English'),
('Real GT Racing Simulator', 3543, 'Real GT Racing Simulator offers the ultimate driving experience for racing enthusiasts. Get behind the wheel of meticulously detailed cars and race on stunningly realistic tracks. Compete in high-speed circuits, fine-tune your vehicle for peak performance, and rise through the ranks to become a true racing legend. This game emphasizes authentic driving physics, customizable cars, and a variety of racing modes&amp;mdash;from casual races to full championship tournaments. Perfect for players who crave a true motorsport challenge, Real GT Racing Simulator will test your skills and precision on every corner.', 'WASD - move esc - pause', 'English'),
('Plinker', 3544, 'Plinker is a fast-paced and addictive game where players drop a ball and guide it through a maze of obstacles. The goal is to hit and destroy as many blocks as possible, earning points with each successful hit. After each turn, players are presented with a choice of two powerful upgrades to strategically enhance their gameplay and maximize their score. This strategic element adds depth and replayability, encouraging players to experiment and find the most effective combinations for achieving the highest score.', 'Use your touch mouse to place the ball in the best spot release your finger to drop the ball', 'English'),
('Forest Camp Adventure', 3545, 'Step into the thrilling world of Forest Camp, a challenging escape game set in a dense, dangerous woodland. As a player, youll need to secure territories while avoiding the sly and stealthy wolf prowling about. The objective is simple yet exciting &amp;ndash; conquer as much land as possible without getting caught by the lurking predator.', 'Navigating through Forest Camp requires quick thinking and smart strategies Use your mouse or keyboard arrow keys to move your character around the forest Observe the wolfs movements take carefully calculated risks and secure areas by leaving your mar', 'English'),
('Save the Sprunki', 3546, 'Sprunki is in danger! A swarm of hostile bees is on the attack, and it&amp;rsquo;s up to you to protect this adorable companion. With just a simple touch of your finger, draw a protective barrier to shield Sprunki from harm. Your creation must hold strong for 7 seconds&amp;mdash;if Sprunki stays safe, you&amp;rsquo;ll advance to the next level! But that&amp;rsquo;s not all&amp;mdash; as you progress, the challenges intensify, and new fascinating characters await your rescue. Put your brain to the test with endless creative puzzles and exciting levels! Do you have what it takes to Save the Sprunki?', 'mouse touch controls', 'English'),
('X O Battle', 3547, 'X-O Battle is the perfect choice for players who enjoy fast-paced puzzle games and strategic challenges. With its combination of classic gameplay, modern design, and mobile compatibility, it provides an exciting and immersive gaming experience for casual players and puzzle lovers alike. Whether youre looking for a fun way to pass the time or aiming to become the ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe champion, this game offers endless entertainment. Play now and enjoy the ultimate Tic-Tac-Toe challenge anytime, anywhere!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Easter Block Puzzle', 3548, 'Easter Block Puzzle is a fun, relaxing block-matching game with a festive Easter theme! Arrange colorful pastel blocks shaped like Easter eggs to clear rows and score points. With simple yet addictive gameplay, enjoy a delightful springtime challenge filled with bunnies, flowers, and cheerful decorations. Can you reach the highest score and complete all the levels? Play now and celebrate Easter with this joyful puzzle adventure!', 'Easter Block Puzzle is a simple yet addictive puzzle game where players place blocks on a grid to complete rows or columns and clear them for points Whether you are playing on a PC or mobile device the controls are easy to learn and make for a fun rela', 'English'),
('Office Escape to Date', 3549, 'You have a date after work, but theres a catch: you need to get ready without your boss catching you! Complete your tasks, and prepare for your date before time runs out. But be careful, if the boss appears, quickly close the activity to avoid getting caught and return to work. How fast can you escape the office and be ready in time?', 'Mouse Only', 'English'),
('Cute Baby Pet Care', 3550, 'Welcome to the world of pet care game. In this game for girls, children will embark on an exciting journey full of responsibility, empathy, and fun. A cute puppy is waiting for your care. You can start by helping it build a cute little nest of its own. The dog has a lot of wounds on its body and you need to help it with its wounds.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Kids Cooking Fun', 3551, 'This is a cooking game for girls. Do you usually like to cook for yourself? Have you ever thought of opening your restaurant? If you are interested in all this, you cant miss our game. The game has 6 modes, allowing you to make all kinds of delicious dishes. You may make the style of ice cream and drinks your guests want, according to their needs.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Multiplayer Team Death Match', 3552, 'Hello Dear players in this game you will challenge your friends in multiplayer team death match, hope you enjoy this game and thanks', 'WASD Movement LMB amp RMB Aim and Shoot R Reload LShift Run Space Jump', 'English'),
('Space Escape Run', 3553, 'This game is completely like story based. One Spaceship is going to blast so you are going to see alert saying that this space ship is going to blast in few minutes. After that your game play levels will start.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fortune Town Slot game 2025', 3554, 'Fortune Town is a slot game based on the number of players who have searched for information about Fortune Tower, it doesnt seem to be a very popular slot. However, this doesnt mean its bad. We encourage you to try it out or check out our list of popular casino games. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sink or Float', 3555, 'Embark on a fascinating journey into the world of physics with Sink or Float. This game is designed to challenge a youngsters understanding of buoyancy and mass in an entertaining way. The player is presented with various objects and their task is to predict whether these objects will sink or float when dropped into water. Each correct answer earns the player points, making the game engaging and educational.', 'To play Sink or Float players need to use their mouse or if playing on a touch device their finger to select an object Once an object is selected they must decide whether it will sink or float when submerged in water To make this decision players', 'English'),
('Car Stunts   Impossible Track', 3556, 'Car Stunts - Impossible Track Challenge gives a thrilling driving experience game that will make you feel proud of real car driving in the sky. Drive car with top speed in this real car racing on hard tracks with extremely fast speed race on the slim track in this Car Stunts - Impossible Track Challenge Game. The Tracks which you play feels like real racing path car driving experience while driving the car you can see different narrow race tracks caves &amp;amp; track high as well landing experience. Show your extreme car driving game 3D skills and you will become the pro in car racing skills.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Endless Sprunki', 3557, 'Play Endless Sprunki and try to reach the best possible record! The goal of the game is really simple: You have to throw the ball from one platform to another one but try to Sprunki not fall out! It could be seems easy but the distance changes with each shot so try to be as accurate as possible and dont make a mistake! Have fun in this cute endless Sprunki game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Whiff Whaff', 3558, 'Get ready to continue enjoying the timeless and traditional game. In this game, you will encounter features that resemble other whiff-whaff games you have played. For example, the ball will accelerate when it hits the platform. You need to be careful with the position of the platform as the speed increases. If you do not catch the ball, your opponent will earn a point.', 'Press A to move the paddle left or D to move it right or just move the mouse around The boosted game mode offers some power-ups you can take or should avoid Respin the ball when its possible by just pressing the SPACEBAR The aim of the game is to sc', 'English'),
('Flag Runner', 3559, 'Flag Runner &amp;zwj; Dash, dodge, and sprint through epic obstacle courses in Flag Runner! &amp;zwj; Grab flags, leap over barriers, and outrun challenges in this fast-paced endless runner! Race through vibrant city streets, jungle trails, and futuristic highways! Can you be the ultimate flag champion? Swipe, jump, and slide&amp;mdash;run like never before! Endless Running Fun Fast-Paced Action Epic Power-Ups Challenging Obstacles Compete for High Scores Unlock Cool Characters', 'Use W A S D Directional keys for Jump left down slide and right respectively Use Space Bar for jump', 'English'),
('Super Sprunki', 3560, 'Embark on a thrilling platforming adventure with Super Sprunki! Inspired by classic games like Super Mario, this game challenges you to navigate vibrant levels filled with tricky obstacles, hidden secrets, and exciting enemies. Jump, run, and collect coins as you guide Sprunki through a colorful world packed with fun surprises. Perfect for fans of retro platformers, this game offers simple controls, engaging gameplay, and a nostalgic yet fresh experience for players of all ages. Can you conquer every level and help Sprunki become a true platforming hero? Dive in and start your adventure today!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Love Tile Trio', 3561, 'Welcome to the Valentines Day tile matching game! Your mission is to match and clear tiles from the board. Tap a tile and move it to an empty space or a spot with a matching tile. If no matches are available or theres no room, youll need to try again. With a countdown timer and tricky puzzles, can you beat the Love Tile challenge?', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this lovely game', 'English'),
('Oddball Detective', 3562, 'In Oddball Detective, identify the element that doesn&amp;rsquo;t belong in each scene. Use your observation skills and knowledge to explore diverse scenes and spot the out-of-place element.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Bracelet Rush', 3563, 'Welcome to Bracelet Rush! This is a challenging and fun parkour adventure game. You will control a crystal bracelet through different platforms and run fast. Collect more beads for a beautiful bracelet. Every step is thrilling and fun. The track is full of obstacles like ducks and milk cartons.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ellie and Friends Venice Carnival', 3564, 'Step into the glamorous world of Venice Carnival Dressup with Ellie and Friends Venice Carnival, where you can join Ellie and her friends at one of the most extravagant events of the year. The Venice Carnival is all about stunning masks, luxurious costumes, and endless glamour, and now you get to help Ellie and her friends get ready for the big celebration! Design unique looks and create the perfect carnival style with a variety of costumes, accessories, and masks.', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Geometry Rash But MCraft', 3565, 'Survive in the Geometry Dash world by jumping as fast and reflexively as possible, but make sure not to hit any obstacles. Collect all the diamonds. Gather the diamonds and carefully reach the portal at the end of the level. Be very careful in the MCraft world and collect the diamonds. Ride the flying mining cart and fly as accurately as possible.', 'To play the game and jump simply click Click with the mouse or your finger Collect diamond to buy costumes from the shop Reach the portal to pass the levels', 'English'),
('Ratomilton Red Light Green Light', 3566, 'Step into the world of Ratomilton Red Light Green Light, a thrilling game of action, timing, and quick reflexes! You take on the role of Rato Milton, a brave little character who must reach the finish line while avoiding detection from a squid game enemy. Inspired by the classic childhood game, this version adds a unique twist, requiring players to master precise movement and perfect their sense of timing to succeed. How to Play The rules are simple but the challenge is real! Your objective is to cross the finish line without being caught moving by the enemy. The game follows a Red Light, Green Light mechanic: - Hold the mouse button to make', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Rescue Dog', 3567, 'Rescue Dog is a fun and engaging puzzle game where your goal is to free the trapped dog from its cage. Each level presents a unique challenge, requiring you to carefully plan your moves to unlock the gate. Using the limited moves displayed on the screen, you must figure out the correct sequence to release the dog. As you progress, the puzzles become more complex, testing your logic and problem-solving skills. Can you rescue the dog in every level? Play now and put your puzzle-solving abilities to the test!', 'Tap on the game screen to play this game', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Poca Avatar Life', 3568, 'This is a doll placement game for girls. You dont have a specific task or goal and can interact with any character and item in the scene. In the at-home section, you will find a variety of amenities and activity places. You can cook and cook with the characters, enjoy the sunshine on the balcony, and even take a bath together.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
