('Sponge Challenge', 3570, 'In Sponge Challenge, you command a bouncy, yellow sponge through a captivating 2D puzzle platform adventure. Your mission is to guide the flexible sponge in collecting precious purple diamonds while maneuvering through levels packed with obstacles and devious traps. Each stage presents a unique puzzle that requires you to leverage the sponges sticky abilities to climb walls, jump between surfaces, and discover the perfect path to the magical portal that leads to subsequent levels. The complexity of each level increases as you progress, requiring both precision and quick thinking.', 'Sponge Challenge employs simple yet engaging controls Tap the screen to make your sponge jump Utilize walls and platforms strategically to alter your direction mid-air allowing you to navigate through each level rsquo s obstacles and traps effectively', 'English'),
