('Squid Escape Game 2Player', 3635, 'You must escape from this iron-covered labyrinth prison. Both blue players need to escape the prison. You must collect all the geometric shapes. Collect all the shapes and find both keys. Find the keys and run to the door. Be very careful, there are thorny obstacles on the ground. Dont stray too far from your friend; if you lose each other, you will lose the game.', 'Use the WASD keys and the Arrow keys to move Both players must reach the door safely and complete the level You must collect all the shapes in the level', 'English'),
('Sweet Baby Clean House', 3636, 'This is a cleaning game for girls. If you usually like to clean your room, our game is designed for you. From bedrooms and living rooms to kitchens and bathrooms, there are many different spaces to clean. Children will become familiar with different cleaning tools and learn about the beauty and differences between a clean room compared to a messy one.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tafl: viking chess', 3637, 'A Scandinavian strategy board game that was popular in the Middle Ages. In Scandinavian society, it was comparable to chess. The game has game variants that differ in: - board size: 7, 9, 11, 13 - victory conditions: bring the king to the edge or corner of the board. - king encirclement conditions: from two or four sides. - the number of attacking (black) and defending (white) pieces. You can play the game with artificial intelligence, with another person on one device, or with an opponent online in multiplayer mode. The attacking black pieces move first. Then the players move in turns. All pieces move vertically or horizontally to any num', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fit Race Game', 3638, 'Hey Gamers, lets play body fun race and make the body from fat to fit instantly and see the cool and funny body shapes by just collecting different amount of calories foods and see the impact instantly. But Its not just a fun body race, there are lot of body weight challenges, which you have to achieve by eating right food items, For instance, if you want to gain weight, you have to eat burgers, sandwiches, ice-cream and milk etc. and similarly eat cucumbers, tomatoes and broccoli to loss your weight. So, You have to choose your diet wisely to achieve your goal and win the level.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Building Mods For Minecraft', 3639, 'Building Mods For Minecraft is the ultimate game for those who love to build and fight. If you&amp;rsquo;re a Minecraft fan looking for a new adventure, this game takes the building mechanics of Minecraft to the next level, combining construction with action. You&amp;rsquo;ll have access to a wide range of building tools and guns.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Love Shopping Rush', 3640, 'Blend cross dressing and parkour, gently shake your fingers .GO! Avoid deadly obstacles all the way, buy your favorite clothes and hair, and dress up for a date! Game features: 1. creative dress up 2. Classic obstacle avoidance 3. easy and challenging', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki VS Pirates', 3641, 'Sprunki Vs Pirates is an exciting sports game to play for all ages. Get into this technical game that tests your aiming ability to make a goal. The challenge is simple yet thrilling: how long can you stay in the game? Your endurance is determined by how well you can aim. Calculate the right angle and degree of force and launch the Ninja through into the basket! In Sprunki Vs Pirates, you need to master the art of precision. Each level presents new obstacles and challenges, ensuring that the game remains engaging and stimulating.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Coloring Music Anime', 3642, 'Collection of coloring pages Sprunki Incredibox, The new video game has captivated users from all over the world. Unleash your creativity with Incredibox Sprunki Coloring! Dive into a fun and relaxing coloring experience featuring unique Sprunki-inspired designs. Perfect for all ages, this app lets you explore your artistic side while bringing your favorite characters to life with vibrant colors. Start coloring today!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Nextbots on Minecraft Squid Game Sprunki', 3643, 'Nextbots are AI-controlled characters that chase and interact with players in a thrilling and dynamic way. In this unique Minecraft experience, Nextbots are themed around the popular Squid Game series and the chaotic, quirky Sprunki meme character. Squid Game Nextbots: Dive into the intense atmosphere of the Squid Game universe. Encounter Nextbots modeled after the Red Light, Green Light doll, masked guards, and even the Front Man. Each Nextbot has unique behaviors and challenges: the doll freezes you if you move at the wrong time, and guards might surround you with deadly precision. Try to survive the games as you navigate various Squid', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Blocks: Fill and Clear', 3644, 'Enter the world of strategic puzzles with our exciting game! Fill the board with random blocks, collect lines and clear the space to score as many points as possible. Inspired by the classic Tetris, the game offers unique modes: Classic: test yourself in endless mode. Timed: manage to score maximum points in a limited time. With bombs: defuse the bomb blocks before they explode. With unique shapes: try to make lines of non-standard shapes. Mixed: a challenge for the most experienced players!', 'Fill the field with blocks You are given random blocks that need to be placed on the playing field Drag them with the mouse or your finger Collect lines Place blocks to fill horizontal or vertical lines', 'English'),
('Cut the Grass   Cutting Grass', 3645, 'Cutting Grass by moving lawn mower is very interesting game to play in control. Here you have different crops to experience and different lawn mower to play. On every level you are going to see different crop field shapes like you feel real crop.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hole 3d Color Block Game', 3646, 'Move the hole with your one finger and collect all 3D cubes &amp;amp; spheres to complete the level. Avoid different type of colored Obstacles to win easy to play, too hard to master Relax Your Mind The game is very addictive and easy and challenging. There are multiple levels in the Hole 3D Color Block game and you need to collect all the white blocks to reach next higher levels. So stick yourself to get high scores by eating white blocks and completing different levels and avoid obstacles. unlock different skins for the hole with the help of coins you earned 200+ Levels of limitless fun Game Features: - Hole 3D Color Block is free to play. -', 'Move the hole with your finger mouse and collect all 3D cubes amp spheres to complete the level Avoid different type of colored Obstacles to win', 'English'),
('Hamster Escape: Prison', 3647, 'An innocent hamster is trying to escape from prison. Help him, because alone it is very difficult. Solve puzzles and tasks of skill and skill to reach your goal so that the hamster can return to his family!', 'Help Hamster escape from prison by solving puzzles and passing reaction tests The game has a tutorial that will not leave you in trouble', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Spot It Find The Difference', 3648, 'Get ready to put your observation skills to the test in Spot It: Find The Difference. This exciting puzzle game challenges you to spot the differences between two seemingly identical images! You&amp;rsquo;ll need sharp eyes and quick thinking to find all the hidden discrepancies! Earn gold and buy extra items or tips to help you navigate the various levels! Can you find all the differences before time runs out?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Trump Wobble Walk Challenge', 3649, 'Trump Wobble Walk Challenge is a hilariously fun ragdoll game packed with crazy and unpredictable challenges. In this quirky walking simulator, your goal is to navigate through massive obstacles and reach the finish line without tumbling over. Each level brings new twists and turns to test your skills and patience. Conquer levels to earn rewards and unlock new flags to customize your gameplay experience. With its humorous mechanics and endless fun, Trump Wobble Walk Challenge is sure to keep you entertained for hours. What are you waiting for? Play the Trump Wobble Walk Challenge NOW and see if you can master the wobble!', 'Arrow keys or mouse to play', 'English'),
('Number Run 3D Casual Game', 3650, 'Number Run 3D is a thrilling casual game that challenges your skills and reflexes as you navigate through a world filled with exciting obstacles.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Rubic Cube', 3651, 'Challenge your mind with the Ultimate Digital Rubiks Cube Simulator! From beginner-friendly 2x2 puzzles to mind-bending 9x9 configurations, this addictive puzzle game lets you test your cube-solving skills across multiple difficulty levels. Start your journey with the classic 3x3 cube or ease into the challenge with a simple 2x2. As your confidence grows, push your limits by tackling increasingly complex configurations - 4x4, 5x5, and all the way up to the ultimate 9x9 challenge. With customizable cube sizes and intuitive touch controls, youre in complete control of your puzzle-solving adventure', 'Use mouse to swipe Use buttons to set dificulty', 'English'),
('Hexa Stack Sort', 3652, 'Hexa Stack Sort is a fun and engaging puzzle game that will put your brain to the test! The goal is simple, but the challenge is exciting. You need to match and stack hexagonal blocks of the same color. You can move the blocks around. but be careful not to get stuck. Only blocks of the same color can be stacked together.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Here Your Pizza', 3653, 'Step into the world of fast-paced pizzeria management Game where your task is to hire employees, serve customers through drive-thru windows, and keep the orders coming at the counter.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Memory', 3654, 'Sprunki Memory offers you to simultaneously train and test your visual memory. Choose a mode: single, passing levels and playing for two. They are essentially identical in that you must quickly find pairs of identical pictures and remove them from the playing field. An interesting version of the game for two, where you will compete with a real opponent to see who can remove all the cards from the field the fastest.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Duo Skibidi 2Player', 3655, 'Two red and blue camera men need to break the toilets. The toilets have risen and want to be broken. Break the blue and red toilets, collect all the money. You must be very careful. Enemies are everywhere and each level is filled with challenges. You can lose at any moment. Break the toilets carefully. Break the blue and red toilets, collect the money, and move to the next level.', 'Use the WASD and Arrow keys to move Jump on the toilets to break them Double jump available Collect all the money', 'English'),
('Cat Freeway', 3656, 'Cute Overload game challenges your reaction skills. The main road is filled with adorable cats moving back and forth, while the side roads are lined with cats waiting for their turn to cross. Your goal is to click at the right moment to let the waiting cats into the main road without causing any collisions. Help all the cats safely cross and youll advance to the next level. With cute graphics and simple gameplay, Cat Freeway is the perfect game to play anywhere and anytime. Are you up for the challenge? Download Cat Freeway now and let the feline fun begin!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Castle Wars: Cell Battle', 3657, 'Dive into an exciting strategy game! You will find a map divided into segments, full of obstacles and enemies of different levels. Use coins to place your heroes: warriors, mages, archers, dragons or catapults. Each character has unique abilities that will help in the fight against opponents. Earn coins by destroying enemies and barriers to buy new heroes and strengthen your army. The games special feature is the ability to combine characters of the same level, creating stronger fighters to defeat powerful opponents.', 'Start by choosing a hero use coins to place warriors mages archers dragons or catapults on the map Drag characters to empty segments to block enemies and destroy obstacles', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Warden of the Crypt', 3658, 'Enter the dark and mystical world of Warden of the Crypt, where you take on the role of a mighty wizard sworn to defend an ancient crypt from waves of ruthless invaders. Use your magical powers strategically to cast powerful spells, outsmart your enemies, and collect dropped items from defeated foes to aid in your survival. Each battle tests your skills as you face increasingly challenging enemies, relying on quick thinking and arcane mastery to protect the crypts secrets. Can you hold the line and keep the darkness at bay?', 'The game can be controlled by touchscreen on mobile devices The game can be controlled using the arrow keys on a computer The game can be controlled with a mouse on a computer', 'English'),
('Kitty Couple Lovely Valentine', 3659, 'Celebrate love with the adorable kitty duo Angela and Tom in Kitty Couple Lovely Valentine. This charming game takes players on a delightful journey filled with fashion, hidden surprises, and puzzles. Help the cute couple prepare for their special Valentine&amp;rsquo;s Day by dressing them up, uncovering hidden hearts, and completing their couple photo puzzle.', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Sprunki Wood Cutter', 3660, 'Welcome to Sprunki Wood Cutter, where your lumberjack skills are put to the test as you chop wood and dodge branches! Think it&amp;rsquo;s an easy task? Think again! While the gameplay is simple to grasp, mastering it is a whole different challenge. With two variable environments and 4 Sprunki characters, the excitement never ends! So grab your axe, rush through the forest, and chop those trees as fast as you can! Sprunki Wood Cutter offers a one-touch control system, addictive gameplay, and a nostalgic arcade-style experience that&amp;rsquo;s completely free!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('World of Military Tanks', 3661, 'Choose your tank and go on the attack! Become the best tank driver! An exciting tank action game. Choose your tank and go ahead to complete missions and destroy enemies. The game has different missions, base defense missions, survival and 5v5 battles. There is a large selection of tanks in the game, buy and upgrade tanks. Complete the missions and get rewarded! The game will be interesting to everyone who is interested in military topics!', 'The goal of the game is to complete the mission objective destroy enemy tanks To shoot point the scope at the tank and right-click When the target is captured the scope will turn red Shoot when a red circle appears in the scope', 'English'),
('Danboard Adventure', 3662, 'Embark on a heartwarming journey with Danboard Adventure, a game filled with story-driven puzzles and fun adventures. As you guide Danboard through exciting challenges, you&amp;rsquo;ll make crucial choices that shape the journeys outcome. Each choice leads to a different adventure! At first, Danboard was fishing when he noticed that his boat was on top of a whale.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Feeding Fun', 3663, 'Feeding Fun is an electrifying puzzle game that challenges players to connect circuits and light up bulbs using limited moves. Set in a futuristic neon world, players must strategically connect energy sources to light up all the bulbs on each level. With increasingly complex puzzles, Feeding Fun offers hours of brain-teasing fun, testing your logic and problem-solving skills.', 'Objective Connect all the kids and foods Controls Tap and drag to connect the kids and foods Ensure all kids are connected before running out of moves', 'English'),
('Truck Parking Game', 3664, 'Game Play: Use arrows for moving truck: To Front: Press Up Arrow to move forward the truck To Back: Press T to shift the gear to reverse and press Up Arrow To left : Left Arrow To Right: Right Arrow Cargo truck parking games 2025 suits you perfectly. This heavy truck parking simulator 2025 is the ultimate simulation &amp;amp; truck parking game with highest graphics ever! If you think that you have all those pro skills of the best driver, then you can enjoy the game must.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('When Sprunki Meet Squid Game', 3665, 'Sprunki X Squid Game Incredibox is an exciting and creative mash-up concept that combines the unique music-making gameplay of Incredibox with the intense and iconic aesthetic of Squid Game. In this crossover, players get to build their own rhythms and beats inspired by the thrilling themes of the survival game show.', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Love Shopping Run', 3666, 'Come and join Love Shopping Run for a crazy shopping parkour adventure. You&amp;rsquo;ll dash through bustling streets and exciting malls in this fast-paced arcade game. Keep running and collect money to buy beautiful clothes. Choose beautiful dresses, hair, and shoes to create an attractive image and you will have more followers.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Falling Ball: Bounce and Break', 3667, 'Welcome to the exciting world of jumping! In this game, you control a ball that must overcome many obstacles and traps. The blocks on the balls path contain free spaces that you need to fly through to continue moving. But be careful: traps lurk at every step, and one wrong move will lead to failure. Your goal is to guide the ball through all the blocks, collect the maximum number of points and, ultimately, get into the basket. For each successful flight between the blocks, you get points. And if you can overcome several blocks in a row without stopping, your points are multiplied!', 'Mouse click orControl the ball to guide it through the free spaces on the blocks and get into the basket at the end of the level Avoid the traps otherwise the game is over Basic rules Avoid the traps - they are on the blocks Getting into a trap ends', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Anime Blade', 3668, 'Colorful anime beauties are waiting for you! Fight in battles, earn points and become the best! If you like Anime and katana fighting, then you definitely should play this game! There are many images of anime girls waiting for you, for whom you can play and fight with them. A large selection of weapons in the game! Different missions and game modes!', 'Computer management Mouse - look around WASD - movement Space Bar - jump Left Shift - run The left mouse button is a blow E - pick up the item P - pause C - sit down Hold Tab - select a weapon 1-2 - next previous weapon', 'English'),
('Flip Shoot Control', 3669, 'Flip Shoot Control is an action-packed arcade game that takes you on an exciting journey to face off against relentless enemies. Key Features: Gunplay: Take control of a powerful gun as you face waves of formidable foes. Sharpen your shooting', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki ShootFly', 3670, 'Fly high with Sprunki in this action-packed shooting game! Take control of a rocket-powered adventure where you dodge obstacles, aim, and shoot down enemies to earn points and extra lives. Perfect for fans of arcade-style games, this exciting experience tests your reflexes, strategy, and aim. Blast through levels, unlock achievements, and climb the leaderboard in this fast-paced and thrilling challenge. With colorful visuals, simple controls, and endless excitement, this game is perfect for kids, casual players, and arcade enthusiasts. Can you help Sprunki conquer the skies and take down all the enemies? Join the fun today!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki SuperHero', 3671, 'Enjoy the Sprunki World with this new SuperHero game. Immerse yourself in the beats and music simulation, create the band and songs, and discover the dark secrets of your favorite characters as Sprunk iron man, Sprunki spiderman, and many others. Enjoy the good and evil world, edit your tracks and experiment with different game modes and characters types to defeat Sprunki thanos.', 'Easy to understand Nice and addictive gameplay Music creation Creativity system Cute HD Graphics Relaxing gameplay Use the Touch or mouse to drag the characters and activate the music', 'English'),
('Coffee Run 3D', 3672, 'Coffee Run 3D is a fun and fast-paced arcade game where you collect coffee items like cups and green coffee liquid while avoiding traps. Slide the collector along a conveyor belt, grow your coffee stack, and test your timing and precision in this exciting challenge!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Ball Juggling', 3673, 'How many times can you juggle these two soccer balls? How to play: Tap the left side of the screen to kick the left football. Tap the right side of the screen to kick the right football. Don&amp;rsquo;t let the balls fall! Warning: This game is highly addictive! Meet Sprunki - your quirky sidekick! Sprunki&amp;rsquo;s always cheering you on with wild antics and funny comments as you juggle! The more you play, the crazier Sprunki gets, offering silly tips and goofy distractions that make the game even more fun. Keep those balls in the air... and see how long you can last before Sprunki cracks you up!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Grab Mario Adventure', 3674, 'Begin an exciting new adventure with Mario in Grab-Mario Adventure! This is a fun platform jumper game that will keep you returning for more. Jump, run, and collect coins as you navigate a world of monsters and obstacles.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Noob Parkour Challenge 3D', 3675, 'The ultimate platformer game where agility, precision, and creativity come together for an exhilarating experience! Dive into a vibrant 3D world filled with thrilling challenges, tricky obstacles, and endless opportunities to showcase your parkour prowess. Whether youre a casual gamer looking for fun or a hardcore player aiming for perfection, this game is designed to keep you hooked. A Journey of Noob to Pro Take on the role of a quirky noob character and embark on an epic parkour adventure. If you love games that combine strategy, precision, and creativity, Noob Parkour Challenge 3D is perfect for you. Each level is a thrilling puzzle.', 'WASD For Movement Mouse For Direction', 'English'),
('Math Challenge For Kid', 3676, 'Math Challenge For Kids is an engaging educational game designed to boost math skills through quick-paced puzzles! Perfect for children learning basic arithmetic, this game offers: 3 Difficulty Levels: Easy (addition/subtraction), Medium (includes multiplication), Hard (adds division) Progressive Scoring: Earn points for correct answers, lose points for mistakes Time Pressure: Solve problems before the timer runs out Visual Feedback: Colorful popups for correct/wrong answers Kid-Friendly: No background music for focused learning Safe Ads: Non-intrusive ads appear every 5 answers (game auto-pauses during ads)', 'Mouse Touchscreen Click Tap difficulty buttons Easy Medium Hard to start Select answers by clicking tapping number options Use the pause button to stop resume gameplay During Ads Game auto-pauses during advertisements', 'English'),
('Sugar Rush', 3677, 'Welcome to Dessert Tapper! A fun and addictive casual game where your quick fingers and sharp eyes will lead you to victory! How to Play: &amp;bull; Tap the delicious desserts to score points and progress through exciting levels! &amp;bull; Be careful not to tap the bombs, or you&amp;rsquo;ll lose your progress! Features: &amp;bull; A wide variety of mouthwatering desserts to discover. &amp;bull; Simple yet challenging gameplay for all ages. &amp;bull; Unlock new levels and test your tapping skills. &amp;bull; Perfect for short bursts of fun or long play sessions. Are you ready to become the ultimate dessert-tapping champion? Download now and start your sweet adventure!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Labo Brick Train Game For Kids', 3678, 'This is an assembly train game for all ages. Do you like small train toys? Have you ever wanted to assemble a beloved train by yourself? You cant miss our game if you are interested in all this.First of all, you need to pick out your favorite train style. Then start assembling the train from the locomotive, followed by the body.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hangman Saga', 3679, 'Enjoy endless word-guessing fun with Hangman Saga! With thousands of levels, each word comes with a helpful category hint to guide you, like Profession for Doctor. Guess the right letters to solve the classic hangman puzzle, but be careful not to make too many mistakes! If you get stuck, use the hint button for extra help. Perfect for word lovers of all ages, Hangman Saga promises endless entertainment and brain-teasing excitement!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to tap the letters guess the words and fill in the blanks to complete the word', 'English'),
('Junkyard Keeper', 3680, 'Enter Junkyard Keeper, where you become the owner of a junkyard. Create amazing new machinery with recycled items. This is a creative simulation game where you will assemble new mechanical equipment by collecting abandoned vehicles and parts. Drive vehicles around the junkyard to collect old parts and transport them back to your base.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Hair Master', 3681, 'This is a hairstyle game for girls. Have you ever wanted to be a fashion hair designer? If you are interested in designing hairstyles, our game is designed for you. Firstly you can choose from a variety of interesting characters who are ready for a new look. Then you need to wash your hair with shampoo and water to get it ready for styling.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Simple Fruit Memory', 3682, 'Simple Memory Game is a fun and engaging memory-matching puzzle where players test their concentration and visual recall across 10 increasingly challenging levels. Each level presents a grid of cards hiding colorful fruit emojis. Players must flip the cards two at a time to uncover matching fruit pairs. The objective is simple: match all the fruit pairs in each level to progress to the next. As levels advance, the number of cards increases, demanding sharper focus and stronger memory skills. Quick recognition and strategic flipping are key to achieving the best possible score.', 'Match the cards for right fruit pairs', 'English'),
('Enchanted Mahjong Saga', 3683, 'Enchanted Mahjong Saga is a fast-paced twist on the classic tile-matching game, with unlimited levels to challenge your mind. Match tiles, beat the clock, and keep your streak alive as each level gets tougher and more exciting. Feeling stuck? Use helpful hints to get back on track and stay in the game.Whether youre playing for a quick break or settling in for a longer session, theres always a new puzzle waiting.', 'Use your mouse or touchpad to select and match tiles', 'English'),
('Foodies 2048', 3684, 'Enter the bright and tasty world of &amp;ldquo;2048 Foodies&amp;rdquo; &amp;mdash; a casual 2048-style puzzle with fruits and berries! Merge identical berries and fruits to create new, juicier, and more delicious sweets. Every merge brings you closer to rare and exotic treats. Simple, intuitive controls make this merge game perfect for everyone: just connect matching items and watch new fruits appear. Colorful, vibrant graphics, smooth animations, and a mouth-watering design create an addictive fruity merge experience.', 'ldquo 2048 Foodies rdquo offers 3 control schemes for any device swipe on mobile hold and drag with the right mouse button or use W A S D or arrow keys All controls are quick responsive and intuitive letting you focus on merging fruits unlock', 'English'),
('Alien Shooting Survival', 3685, 'Alien Shooting Survival throws you into an apocalyptic forest and ruined town overrun by alien creatures and soldier invaders. Armed and ready, you must fight off waves of hostile enemies, from terrifying alien animals to armored troops. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygames.org.es/''&gt;https://www.crazygames.org.es/&lt;/a&gt; . Drive vehicles to navigate deadly zones, reach objectives, and survive relentless battles. Destroy every threat to complete your mission!', 'WASD TO WALK AND DRIVE vehicle and mouse to aim and shooting', 'English'),
('Tic tac toe   with AI and multiplayer', 3686, 'Tic Tac Toe is a classic strategy-based HTML5 game built with pure HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript, designed for desktop and mobile browsers. This lightweight game is responsive, fast-loading, and fully customizable, making it perfect for websites, blogs, and game portals. Players can challenge the computer (AI) or play with a friend in 2-player mode. The game features clean UI, smooth animations, and modern design, ensuring a great user experience across all devices. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a developer, game publisher, or looking to add engagement to your site, this Tic Tac Toe game is an easy-to-integrate, monetizable, and timeless classic.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Space Geometry Dash Waves', 3687, 'Space Geometry Dash Waves is a fast-paced reflex game where precision is everything. Hold the mouse to make your arrow rise, release to glide down&amp;mdash;navigate through a neon-lit maze of moving traps and deceptive geometry. Each of the 40 handcrafted levels introduces a new obstacle mechanic: vanishing ninjas that flicker in and out of sight, hidden barriers that only appear when youre close, and more unpredictable challenges designed to test your timing and focus. From twisting corridors to sudden reveals, every stage pushes your skill to the limit in a hypnotic journey through the horizons of geometry. Can you master the rhythm and reach th', 'mouse only', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Pic Pie Wonders', 3688, 'Pic Pie Wonders&amp;rdquo; is a delightful photo puzzle game where each level presents a round picture broken into pieshaped pieces. Swap two adjacent pieces by swiping with your finger or mouse, and keep rearranging them until the photo is complete.', 'Click and hold or swipe your finger on a pie piece then drag to an adjacent piece to swap them Keep swapping until you complete the round photo', 'English'),
('Maze Evolution', 3689, 'Maze Evolution combines puzzle mazes to make the game more exciting. You start with easy mazes, and as you progress, the levels become harder to complete. Also, the game consists of 28 levels to play.on any device.', 'The game is easy to control For the computers you can use your mouse and on mobile devices you can control it with your touch pen or finger To start the level first you need to touch the black star After you touch the player then you can control it', 'English'),
('Billiard Diamond Challenge', 3690, 'Billiard Diamond Challenge is a fun and free online billiard game for both kids and adults. Your goal is to sink all the balls into the pockets except for the white ball. While playing, you can collect blue diamonds that allow you to unlock a brand new cue. The game offers both level mode and time mode, so you can choose the challenge that suits you best. Get ready to test your skills and have fun at the billiard table!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Cozy Kitchen Merge', 3691, 'Cozy Kitchen Merge is a cute cooking puzzle where you place dishes on the tray, watch the queue, and merge 3 or more of the same dish&amp;mdash;sides or corners both count. Each merge makes the next recipe and bumps your score. Every 100 points gives you an Eat Token. Tap the fork button to munch one dish and make space when things get tight. Keep at least one empty spot; no room for the next dish means game over. Climb the recipe ladder (1&amp;rarr;10), unlock sweet achievements, and chase your best score. Soft art, cozy sounds, quick runs&amp;mdash;perfect for a relaxing break. And hey, please dont wreck the game menu. Things may fall.', 'Tap click an empty spot on tray to place the next dish Check the counter the dish on the right goes next Merge 3 or more of the same dish touching each other Every 100 points you get 1 Eat Token In the main menu you can tap and drag the decor', 'English'),
('FRAGMENT', 3692, 'You are a weaponized human test subject disguised as a robot. Your test is to shoot through the test, destroying the heart behind your creation. There are ~40 levels you have to finish. Try to finish it as fast as possible.', 'A D Move S Slide Space Jump Skip Intro Exit Time Screen Mouse Aim R Reset if you get stuck Right-click Shoot ESC P Pause', 'English'),
('JellyMerge', 3693, 'Slide the screen to merge the jelly blocks of the same color. All of them are combined to complete the level. The game features multiple exquisite levels. Come and challenge your brain.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tralalero Tralala Endless Run', 3694, 'Tralalero Tralala Endless Run is a colorful and exciting online game that kids will love. The challenge is simple but addictive: stay alive for as long as possible while running endlessly through a quirky world full of surprises. Your goal is to jump on jellyfish to keep moving forward and collect as many delicious burgers as you can along the way. The more burgers you gather, the higher your score will climb. But watch out: crashing into the top or bottom of the screen will quickly end your run. This fast-paced adventure is all about quick reflexes, timing, and endless fun. Perfect for kids who enjoy bright graphics, silly characters, and non-stop action. Best of all, it is completely free to play online, so you can jump right into the excitement anytime. So, get ready to guide Tralalero Tralala through this hilarious endless journey, collect those burgers, and see how long you can survive. Can you set a new record? Give it a try and have fun!', 'Left and right arrow keys or mouse to play', 'English'),
('Pin Away Puzzle   Tap It Out', 3695, '**Pin Away Puzzle &amp;mdash; Tap It Out: What&amp;rsquo;s Inside?** Dive into a world of captivating challenges, where every stage is a new test of your logic and problem-solving abilities. With a variety of unique pin arrangements, each level offers a fresh and exciting experience. Engage in effortless tapping action thats both fun and rewarding, as you plan your moves and clear the board with precision. Whether youre seeking a way to relax or looking to boost your mental agility, this game offers the perfect solution.', 'Exercise your mind by tapping on pins of various shapes taking into account each step since some pins might be obstructed by others Brace yourself for a delightful and effortless adventure that blends tactics and calmness', 'English'),
('Physics: Electro Magnetism Quiz', 3696, 'Check out this Physics: Electro-magnetism quiz from Immanitas. This is good for students or educators who just want a quiz test of their basic knowledge of this topic of Physics. Winning-streak is taken account of!', 'Select the CORRECT option', 'English'),
('Something below the Sea Hard version', 3697, 'A team of scientists spotted an area of the planet with an immense amount of garbage, seeing that this threatened marine life, they decided to create drones to remove this garbage, but something else is hidden...', 'Use ASDW for move or Touch and shoot with P ou Touch the square for shoot', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fruit Merge 2048 &amp;ndash; Juicy Puzzle', 3698, 'Fruit Merge 2048 is a fun and addictive puzzle game that combines the classic 2048 gameplay with colorful, mouth-watering fruits! Simply swipe to merge identical fruits and watch them evolve into bigger, juicier ones. The more you merge, the closer you get to the ultimate fruit! Featuring bright graphics, smooth animations, and satisfying gameplay, this fruit puzzle is perfect for casual players and puzzle lovers of all ages. Whether you want to challenge your brain, pass the time, or just enjoy some juicy fun, Fruit Merge 2048 is your go-to choice.', 'Use arrow keys or swipe to move tiles Combine matching fruits to create new ones', 'English'),
('Little Princess Dress Up', 3699, 'This is a fashion dress-up game for girls. If you like to dress up virtual dolls, we have a game you cant miss. The game offers a wide range of styles of gorgeous outfits and accessories for you to choose from, so you will be overwhelmed.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Dont Tease Me', 3700, 'Don&amp;rsquo;t Tease Me is a survival game where dodging is your only defense. Avoid balls, grab ghost pickups to vanish, and see how long you can stay masked. No fighting back&amp;mdash;just pure evasion!', 'Use WASD Keys or Left Mouse Click or Touch to control the character to avoid the incoming stones', 'English'),
('Jam Escape', 3701, 'Parking Guru is an addictive parkingpuzzle game where you rearrange vehicles to clear a path for the red car to escape the jam. If you&amp;rsquo;re a fan of the classic Rush Hour board game, this puzzle will hook you instantly! Levels for every skill: From simple shuffles to mind-bending brainteasers. Varied vehicle roster: Classic sedans, rugged SUVs, and massive trucks&amp;mdash;all with unique silhouettes. Intuitive controls: Drag cars with your mouse, rotate them, and find your way out of even the most tangled traffic. Time &amp;amp; move tracking: Beat your best time or take it slow&amp;mdash;set a new personal record or simply enjoy the challenge. Vibrant art', 'Play levels in sequence or jump straight to any level you choose Drag cars with your mouse to clear a path for the red car Aim to solve each puzzle with the fewest moves and in the shortest time Click ldquo Reset rdquo to restart the current level', 'English'),
('HexaMatch', 3702, 'HexaMatch &amp;ndash; The Ultimate Number Puzzle! Swipe and sort tiles into the empty slot to solve addictive hexa puzzles. With progressive difficulty, unique gameplay, and a fresh twist on classic number games, HexaMatch is perfect for all ages. Train your brain, relax your mind, and enjoy endless fun with this simple yet challenging merge hexa puzzle!', 'You have only one empty slot on the board Slide a tile into the empty slot to move it Tap or swipe the tile you wish to move Keep moving the tiles until all the numbers are in the correct sequence', 'English'),
('Physics: Heat Temperatuie Quiz', 3703, 'Try out our new Quiz on Heat and Temperature in Physics. This quiz is designed for a quick checkpoint about your knowledge on this topic. Prepare well and then try :)', 'Click on the CORRECT option', 'English'),
('Rocket Adventure', 3704, 'Blast off for the stratosphere with Rocket Adventure, the addictive physics rocket game that beat all conquest games. Your mission is to launch your rocket as high into orbit as possible. Simple touches control when you release each stage in your rocket. Earn in-game currency from successful launches and spend it to acquire new parts and styles.', 'Use the mouse or touch to play', 'English'),
('Balloon Heroes Run and Rise', 3705, 'Balloon Heroes: Run &amp;amp; Rise is a fast-paced racing game where you compete in thrilling obstacle courses. Collect balloons to power high jumps, avoid falling into water, and race to the finish line ahead of rivals. Earn coins to unlock skins and customize your hero. With tons of challenging levels, this game offers nonstop action, strategy, and fun as you run, jump, and outsmart opponents to claim victory!', 'Tap or mouse click to play', 'English'),
('Mysterious elevator', 3706, 'Immerse yourself in the thrilling adventure of &amp;ldquo;Mysterious Elevator&amp;rdquo;! You are trapped in a skyscraper with 100 floors, ruled by the sarcastic Keeper of Numbers &amp;mdash; a master of mathematical riddles. To escape, solve logical challenges while riding in an old creaky elevator. Swap number and sign blocks, assemble equations, and face extra puzzles along the way. Each floor is a new test: from simple arithmetic to tricky logic traps. One mistake, and the elevator may crash! With every solution you descend closer to freedom. &amp;ldquo;Mysterious Elevator&amp;rdquo; is perfect for fans of math, logic, and atmospheric mysteries. Can you outsmart the Keeper and escape?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Maths for Standard II', 3707, 'Add the numbers and choose the correct option. This is simple maths game for giving puzzles to students who are below or in Standard 2nd. This just asks students to choose from 4 options out of which one option is CORRECT!', 'Click to choose an option out of 4 options', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Cowboy Shooter', 3708, 'Step into the Wild West and test your aim in this fast-paced cowboy shooting game! Time is running, and every shot counts. Break bottles, hit targets, and challenge yourself to earn the highest score before the clock runs out. With simple yet addictive gameplay, Cowboy Shooter offers endless fun and a true test of your reflexes. Are you quick enough to become the ultimate sharpshooter?', 'Aim Move the mouse to aim at the targets Shoot Press the Left Mouse Button to fire Mobile Use the on-screen buttons to aim and shoot just like on PC', 'English'),
('Multiplication Master', 3709, 'Multiplication Master isn&amp;rsquo;t your average math game &amp;ndash; it&amp;rsquo;s a full-on battle for brainpower. You pick the mode, you set the pace. From steady Normal runs to the nerve-wracking Timed Challenge, the lightning-fast Quick Answers, the relentless Survival, the explosive Bomb Mode, and the ultimate Marathon &amp;ndash; every match will push your limits. Think you&amp;rsquo;ve got the tables from x2 to x12 locked down? Prove it. Mix them up for the real test. Rack up points, keep those streaks alive, and climb the global leaderboard where only the sharpest minds survive.', '- Keyboard Touchscreen ndash Type your answer using the number keys or on-screen keyboard - Mouse Tap ndash Click or tap the answer buttons in Quick Answers mode - Press Enter or tap Check to submit your answer - Use Menu buttons to change leve', 'English'),
('ASMR Makeover &amp;amp; Makeup Studio', 3710, 'Get ready to dive into the world of beauty and creativity! ASMR Makeup &amp;amp; Makeover Studio offers an incredible opportunity to give your virtual model a stunning makeover. This isnt just any makeover game &amp;mdash; its an immersive experience that combines relaxation and excitement through the power of ASMR!', 'Give your toy a fabulous new look with these skin care and makeup options Check out what the game has to offer Pamper your dolls skin and make it shine with various skin care products Choose from an array of makeup styles and colors to create any d', 'English'),
('Frog Adventure', 3711, 'Leap, sneak, and strike as a pixel-art ninja frog in a fast-paced platformer adventure! Dive into a stylish retro world where you control a ninja frog with lightning reflexes. Each level is crafted to challenge your timing, precision, and creativity. Jump over traps, dash through enemies, and master the art of pixel-perfect movement. With vibrant visuals and snappy gameplay, this is platforming with attitude.', 'Controls larr A Q Move Left rarr D Move Right uarr W Space Z Jump TAP Pause', 'English'),
('Wood Nuts Bolts Screw', 3712, 'Step into the world of Wood Nuts &amp;amp; Bolts: Screw Game, where every twist and turn will put your brain to the test! This games creates your thinking world in a unique way of solving puzzles and unscrewing, screwing the nuts &amp;amp; bolts. Each level is more tricky than you experience in the previous level.', 'Tap to play', 'English'),
('Queen Be', 3713, 'Live a royal life, manage your duties, and rule your kingdom with grace and rule your kingdom with grace and rule your kingdom with grace', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Rocket Charge Run', 3714, 'Enjoy an exciting running game in the Rocket Charge Run. Youll run through exciting parkour levels. Avoid obstacles and collect energy boosts. Keep running and collect more batteries. And charge the battery fully. Avoid cutting machines, robots, etc. Use your quick reflexes and parkour skills to avoid crashing and keep your run going.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Arrow Shot Loop', 3715, 'Arrow Shot Loop is an exciting action-packed game where precision and timing are key! Guide your arrows through an endless loop of challenges, aiming for targets while avoiding obstacles. With each level, the difficulty increases, requiring faster reflexes and sharper focus. Collect power-ups to enhance your arrows, and unlock new environments as you progress. Our developer games &lt;a href=''https://www.coolcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.coolcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt; . Compete for the highest score and challenge friends to beat your record. Get ready for a fun and addictive archery experience!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Runner Coaster Race', 3716, 'Do you enjoy roller coasters? In Runner Coaster Race, you will experience the fast roller coaster arcade track, combined with parkour elements of free running. In this real simulation, you must collect passengers on the ring road. Collect money, avoid obstacles like bombs, and push your limits to become the king of the track.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Spikes', 3717, 'Sprunki Spikes is a fun adventure game thats exciting to play. Here is our little color box hero, who has been stuck in the middle of a whole lot of traps. Help him dodge them and navigate through the challenging environment. There are really fast-paced obstacles passing by keep away from them and survive as long as you can. This game will boost your reflexes as you deal with the hardest objects moving toward him. The dynamic and engaging gameplay ensures an adrenaline-pumping experience that will keep you on the edge of your seat. Join the adventure and see how long you can last!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
