('Traffic Racing: Overtake Everyone', 3719, 'Dive into the exciting world of city racing! Choose a car from the garage - each car has unique characteristics and speed. Go to the city with heavy traffic, choosing between one-way or two-way traffic. Your task is to go around other cars, avoid accidents and collect coins to earn as many points as possible. On the way you will find bonuses that will help improve the characteristics of the car or get temporary boosts. The further you drive, the more money you will earn, opening access to new, faster and more powerful cars.', 'Start the game by choosing a car from the garage - each car has its own characteristics Then choose the driving mode one-way or two-way traffic In the city your task is to drive the car going around other cars to avoid collisions', 'English'),
('Flick Master 3D', 3720, 'Ready to become the ultimate Flick Master 3D? In this exciting casual action game, you&amp;rsquo;ll use powerful fingers to precise flicks to conquer various challenges! Your office has been taken over by evil workers. You have to hit them to become the master of the super flick glove. Become a superhero and crush your enemies with deadly blows.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Heaven or Hell  The choice is yours', 3721, 'Distribute souls between heaven and hell! The choice is yours! In the game you have to choose where to send the souls of people! Send sinners to HELL, and the righteous to HEAVEN, dont make a mistake! Well, or vice versa, the choice is yours! Angels and demons will tell you. Its just a fun game. Enjoy and have a fun time. Good luck!', 'Management for mobile devices Hold your finger on the screen to move from side to side Control for PC Hold down the cursor on the screen or use the arrows on the keyboard to move from side to side', 'English'),
('Range Master Sniper Academy', 3722, 'Range Master: Sniper Academy is the ultimate test of your shooting skills! Become a master marksman in this action-packed sniper game. Here precision, timing, and strategy are key. Your objective is to shoot your targets with deadly accuracy and reach the target score. The game consists of multiple levels, each of which is challenging.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
