('Merge Number Cube 3d Run Game', 3724, 'Experience the ultimate combination of 3D running and merge upgrade mechanics in Merge Number Cube: 3D Run Game! Dash through thrilling platforms and collect more cubes. Lead the cube past the obstacles on the run and choose the right gate to raise your team member. Take care to avoid large pendulums, spikes, cutters, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Skibidi Toilet Jigsaw Puzzle', 3725, 'Laugh your way through the hilariously wacky world of Skibidi Toilet Jigsaw! Solve puzzles featuring iconic scenes and characters from the viral meme. Perfect for fans of funny puzzles and quirky humor, this game offers adjustable difficulty levels for all ages. Enjoy hours of entertainment and meme-worthy fun with this unique puzzle game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('THE MAGIC HOUSE', 3726, 'Get ready to design your perfect home in THE MAGIC HOUSE! This immersive drag-and-drop game allows you to unleash your creativity and build a space thats truly yours. Customize every aspect of your home, from the layout to the decor, and create a magical world for you and your furry friends to enjoy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Unblocked Mission ImPossible', 3727, 'In this character-driven mission, your protagonists primary objective is to push a mouse towards a stopping point while facing a continuous downward force thats out of their control. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.kizi10.org/''&gt;https://www.kizi10.org/&lt;/a&gt; As they navigate through the challenging environment, they must also contend with a series of cunning traps that have been strategically placed to impede their progress.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
