('Sprunki s WORLD All MOD', 3728, 'Discover Sprunki Incredibox: A Fan-Made Musical Adventure If youre a fan of Incredibox, youre going to love Sprunki Incredibox! This fan-made mod takes the beloved creativity and music-mixing fun of the original game to exciting new levels. At sprunki.org, were thrilled to present this vibrant and imaginative experience, packed with unique features that make it a must-play for music enthusiasts and gamers alike.', 'mouse and click drag and drop', 'English'),
('Bus Stop: 2048!', 3729, 'Game Features: 1. Unique gameplay allows passengers to board their cars and leave the station. 2. Collect cool cars, unlock and collect cool cars in each level of play. 3. There are many types of cars in the game store, waiting for players to purchase them.', '1 The goal of the game is to distribute passengers to their cars and know how to free all passengers 2 Use tools during the mission to complete the level faster 3 Just click on the car of the same color as the passenger to match them', 'English'),
('Plumber Game', 3730, 'Dive into the ocean and become a plumber of the extreme in Sea Plumber. Put your brain to the trial in this puzzle game, repair the pipes in the deep and become the champion of plumbing. Sea Plumber is an amusing game for the whole family! Only recommended for... everyone!', 'Dive into the ocean and become a plumber of the extreme in Sea Plumber Put your brain to the trial in this puzzle game repair the pipes in the deep and become the champion of plumbing Sea Plumber is an amusing game for the whole family Only recomme', 'English'),
('Draw Bridge Puzzle', 3731, 'Draw Bridge Puzzle Game is an exciting and challenging brain game that will put your problem-solving skills to the test. In this bridge-building adventure, your task is to draw paths for the car to safely navigate through obstacles and reach its destination. Get ready to embark on a thrilling journey of bridge construction and puzzle-solving as you draw roads to rescue the stranded car!', 'Follow the game instructions', 'English'),
('Build Your Vehicle Run', 3732, 'Welcome to Build Your Vehicle Run, an exciting and creative parkour game! In this game, you&amp;rsquo;ll collect different parts including wheels, engines, and other powerful components. Upgrade along the way to make your vehicle faster, stronger, and more unique.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Car Parking Master Puzzle Game', 3733, 'This is the best puzzle game you will ever play! This Car Parking Master Puzzle Game is so much fun. at a time you can feel happy and playable. best 3D controllers arking.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Connect the Pipes: Water Puzzle', 3734, 'Dozens of unique levels await you in this exciting puzzle game, where you need to show your logic and ingenuity! There are pipes, water sources and drains on the playing field. Your task is to turn the pipes so that the water from the source reaches the drain. But thats not all! Water comes in different colors, and to complete some levels you will have to mix the streams, creating new colors. Each drain may require a certain color of water, and the difficulty of the levels will increase, offering new mechanics and challenges.', 'Rotate pipes Tap a pipe on the board to rotate it Connect the water source to the desired drain Mix colors Water comes in different colors If the drain requires a certain color direct the streams from different sources into one pipe to mix them Fil', 'English'),
('Dog Hide N Seek', 3735, 'Embark on an adventurous hide-and-seek game in Dog Hide N Seek! Join a group of playful kids and their furry friend as they hide and seek in a beautifully illustrated forest. Quick reflexes and strategic hiding spots are essential to avoid being seen by the dog. Can you outsmart the dog and emerge as the ultimate hide-and-seek champion?', 'Start the Game Tap the play button to begin your hide-and-seek adventure Move Quickly Tap the screen to make your character walk faster Hide Smartly Avoid being seen by the dog by stopping when the dog is looking in your direction Win the Challenge', 'English'),
('Merge the Coins: USSR!', 3736, 'A game in an unusual setting! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone where coins fall and connect if they are the same! Connect as many coins as possible to get the biggest one, collect points! Become the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect the coins but over time there will be more and more of them Once you connect the biggest coin in this game it will disappear and give you the most points', 'English'),
('Toilet Paper Jam', 3737, 'Welcome to Toilet Paper Jam, a creative and fun brain puzzle game. In this game, your goal is to solve the toilet paper jams. Everyone needs a section of paper. Match similar rolls of toilet paper and use different lengths of paper properly.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
