('Sprunki Money Stack Incredibox', 3740, 'Now Sprunki must gather as much money as possible, collect all the money and multiplied it to buy a new house and upgrades all his life behavior!', 'tap to play', 'English'),
('Sky Corona Evasion', 3741, 'Sky Corona Evasion is an engaging mobile game developed by jojolife that thrusts players into a high-stakes aerial adventure. , this game combines the fast-paced elements of an endless runner with the precision and challenge of flight navigation. Players control an airplane, navigating through a sky filled with various obstacles and virus-like enemies, symbolizing the titular Corona. The primary objective is to achieve the highest possible distance without crashing, demanding quick reflexes and strategic maneuvering.', 'Right-click the mouse and move it', 'English'),
('Lines 98 Old School', 3742, 'Classic puzzle Balls of Lines 98, made in old school style. Move the balls around the field so as to line up 5 balls of the same color in a row. Score points and take the first place in the leaderboard.', 'Control - touch the ball you want to move and with the second touch choose where to move this ball When playing from a computer select a ball with a mouse click and the next click indicate where to move this ball', 'English'),
('Eye Color DIY', 3743, 'This is an eye color art game for girls. Have you ever wondered what would happen if your eyes were a different color? Maybe you have a bold idea and want to make your own eye color and shine.If you want to try these, you cant miss our game. You can start by choosing an eye shape and color base. Then you must use the tools to mix the colors, add patterns, and apply effects.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Animal Name Puzzle', 3744, 'Animal Name Puzzle is an exciting word scramble game where players must rearrange a set of scrambled letters to form the name of an animal. The game offers a fun challenge by testing both word recognition and knowledge of animals, ranging from common pets to rare wild species. If you get stuck, you can use a hint to help you out. For a fresh twist, the shuffle button lets you change the arrangement of the letters, adding variety to each puzzle. Solve them all and discover a world of animals through this engaging word game!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Two Player Stick Steve and Alex', 3745, 'Steve and Alex, the stick figure characters, want to escape from the Nether world. To help them in this adventure, you must be two players. In this two-player game, you must escape from the Nether world with your friend. Be very careful while escaping because monsters are coming from everywhere and they never stop. Reach the portal at the end of the level safely.', 'Use the WASD and Arrow keys to move Avoid the monster at the end of the level and reach the portal at the end Double jump available', 'English'),
('Sprunki Sniper Squid Game', 3746, 'In Sprunki Sniper Squid Game, players must stay still and wait for the sound to stop. Once the sound fades, each character, known as a Sprunki, is marked for elimination. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.playonline.top/''&gt;https://www.playonline.top/&lt;/a&gt; Players must carefully time their movements to avoid becoming a target of the sniper in this tense, strategic game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Real Car Parking And Stunt', 3747, 'Welcome to Real Car Parking And Stunt, a challenging driving simulation game. Here you&amp;rsquo;ll control a car and put your parking and stunt skills to the test. Choose stunt mode or parking mode, each level challenges you to park your car accurately while performing exciting stunts.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Incredible Kids Dentist', 3748, 'This is a dentist game for kids. Have you ever wanted to be a dentist? If this was your dream before, you should not miss this game. In this educational game, you can become a doctor in a hospital. You need to check the teeth of your patients.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Racing Ball Master 3D', 3749, 'Ready for a casual racing adventure? In Racing Ball Master 3D, you control a super-fast rolling ball. You will race against many opponents on a colorful 3D track. The track has obstacles and challenges like spinning windmills, roadblocks, etc. Every step tests your operations and reactions.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Platform Drop', 3750, 'Circle Platform is a fun and addictive online game that tests your timing and precision skills. The objective is simple yet challenging: guide a ball to match and land perfectly on a moving platform. With vibrant visuals and smooth gameplay, Circle Platform keeps you engaged with its dynamic motion and increasing levels of difficulty.As you progress, the game introduces new twists, like faster-moving platforms and obstacles, to keep the gameplay exciting and test your reflexes. Circle Platform is perfect for quick sessions or extended play&amp;mdash;jump in and see how far you can go!', 'Tap or click to release the ball from its starting position Time your release to ensure the ball aligns with the rotating or moving platform Aim for the perfect drop to earn bonus points and unlock higher levels', 'English'),
('Squid Game Match Survival', 3751, 'Experience the thrill of Squid Game Match, a survival-themed puzzle game for fans! Match tiles to progress through levels inspired by the show&amp;rsquo;s challenges. Perfect for those who love strategy games, this unique puzzle experience combines suspense, fun, and creativity. Will you survive the ultimate Squid Game puzzle challenge?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tiles Matching', 3752, 'Free online game Tiles Matching - play in the browser without downloading. It is suitable for the development of logic for both adults and children - an ideal timekiller. Tiles Matching is a puzzle game combining the game mechanics of Mahjong and Three in a Row (Match-3). A logical educational game for children and adults. With each level, the difficulty increases - not everyone can complete the game the first time. Challenge your intelligence.', 'Match 3 blocks of the same element so that they match each other Match and remove all the tiles to complete the level The game has a large number of levels that are becoming more difficult', 'English'),
('Nightmare Couple Eternal Love', 3753, 'Step into the hauntingly beautiful world of Nightmare Couple Eternal Love, where romance and spookiness collide. This unique dress-up game lets you explore gothic fashion, eerie backdrops, and enchanting love between a mysterious couple. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a fan of Halloween aesthetics or captivating storytelling, this game promises an unforgettable experience.', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Spider Fighter', 3754, 'Want to become a superhero and have an action journey? In Spider Fighter, you&amp;rsquo;ll fight against waves of enemies as a Spider-Man. The game includes fast action and fighting elements, and each level is full of excitement and challenge. You can explore open cities in free mode, destroy anything and get rewards.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('2048 Cubes', 3755, 'Endless 2048 game with a twist, blocks with physics. Blocks will colliide and bounce after collision. Drop and merge same numbers to reach higher numbers.', 'Swipe right and left to move the block and release to drop Merge blocks with same number to get a bigger block Increase your score with more blocks Game ends when the board fills up to the dashed line', 'English'),
('Draw Save Puzzles', 3756, 'Draw Save Puzzles is a fun and creative game where you solve puzzles by drawing lines or shapes to guide the Stickman to safety. Each level offers new challenges, testing your logic and problem-solving skills! Explore tons of amazing &amp;amp; challenging levels and try to complete them all. Good luck!', 'Tap or mouse click to play', 'English'),
('Moto Stunt Racing', 3757, 'Get ready to ride, race, and perform bike stunts in the amazing spider hero bike games. This game is all about racing and doing cool stunts on 3d bikes. Riding a gt bike on a Mega ramp and flying through the air, doing flips and bike tricks. Its like being a superhero on two wheels in motorcycle stunt bike race games 2024. Start an amazing adventure of extreme tricky moto stunts on sky-high mega ramps. Accept Motorbike race challenges.Grab your helmet and do the dare to perform extreme stunts on the mega ramps with the superhero motorcycle games 3D. Show your best skills to do the breathtaking stunts and have non-stop action with the spider bike race games 2024. Ride on mega ramps, dodge hurdles and defeat your rivals to be the number one racer of the superhero ramp stunt bike games 3D Ride a superhero mega ramp bike fast! Race against other stunt riders on different tracks. Choose a gt bike in Bike Stunt Games and make it go fast. Pay attention in superhero stunt bike race game track', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
