('Squid Game Sprunki Escaped Backrooms', 3759, 'Now Sprunki has a nightmare. He has transformed to the snake and have to escaped from Backrooms. Unfortunately Squid Game soldier lurking around search for him! Kill them all and escape! good luck', 'WASD Arrow Keys - move Mouse move - camera Space LMB - Head Up E Shift - Toggle Head Up R - Restart P - Pause Menu', 'English'),
('Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box', 3760, 'Welcome to the wonderful world of Huggy Mix Sprunki Music Box. This music game is filled with energy and rhythm. Follow the beats, tap along to the music, and have fun with casual gameplay.You can choose three modes: health, ice, and bad man. You can make unique tunes that reflect your personality.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Launch The Sprunki', 3761, 'Sprunki Launch is an exciting physics-based game where you catapult Sprunki to destroy zombie heads and conquer thrilling challenges! As Sprunki, the fearless hero, you&amp;rsquo;ll launch yourself through spooky, haunted landscapes, aiming to eliminate all zombie heads standing in your way. Strategize your shots, break through tricky obstacles, and unleash powerful combos to clear each level. With increasing challenges, eerie settings, and special power-ups, your goal is simple: destroy all the zombie heads and achieve victory in this action-packed adventure!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Coloring Time', 3762, 'Sprunki Coloring Time is a delightful and free online coloring game perfect for kids! Choose from six fun images and unleash your creativity to craft a masterpiece. Once you&amp;rsquo;re done, share your colorful creation with friends and enjoy the joy of art. Get ready to have a great time coloring and exploring your artistic side!', 'Use mouse to play', 'English'),
('MoneyCollectorUssr!', 3763, 'A game in an unusual setting! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone where coins fall and connect if they are the same!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect the coins but over time there will be more and more of them Once you connect the biggest coin in this game it will disappear and give you the most points', 'English'),
('Gun Shooting   Running Game', 3764, 'Collect bullets Increase the firer rate. Increase number of bullets fire Dodge obstacles, Shoot everything in your path. The longer the bullet stack, the higher your score, Stunning 3D guns and bullets theme Smooth controls for quick lane changes Satisfying gameplay for stress relief.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Block Digger', 3765, 'In Block Digger, Break through rocks, gather precious gems, and upgrade your mine to boost your fortune. Unlock new levels, chase rewards, and build a mining empire like no other. Easy to play, hard to put down&amp;mdash;start digging for treasure now!', 'Tap the screen or click with your mouse to dig', 'English'),
('Overtaking   Traffic Rider', 3766, 'Tap the screen to let the car enter the main road heavy traffic on the street. Control the cars at the corner to enter the main road to ensure that there are no traffic accidents.', 'Tap the screen to let the car enter the main road', 'English'),
('Sprunki in Squid Game Chamber', 3767, 'In the heart of the notorious Squid Game Chamber, there is only one thing on Sprunki&amp;rsquo;s mind: survival. A place where every corner hides a threat, and every move could be their last, the Squid Game Chamber is not a place for the faint of heart. Its a world where tension runs high, and the air is thick with the terror of the unknown. Yet, despite the horror that surrounds them, Sprunki is determined to play the game&amp;mdash;no matter the cost. The game is simple in its premise but deadly in its execution: run, grab the coin, and escape. Sounds easy enough, doesn&amp;rsquo;t it? But in this hellish realm, nothing is ever that simple.', 'WASD - move', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Sprunki Stick', 3768, 'Hey help the Sprunki to stretch the stick the more you can to reach and walk on the platforms. Beware! If the stick is not long enough, you will fall down! Get yourself in the ninja action! How far can you go? Enjoy it!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Witch And Fairy BFF', 3769, 'Two unusual girlfriends - a Fairy and a Witch - study together, although they are so different. Fairy, with her delicate pink outfits and impeccable sense of style, is always ready to offer fashion tips and create vivid images. Her girlfriend-Witch, who prefers a Gothic style, chooses mysterious and gloomy outfits. Players will be able to help both heroines choose outfits for various events: from dancing to magic lessons. Join magical friends in their exciting fashion adventure where style and magic go hand in hand!', 'Depending on the gaming device a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it', 'English'),
('Mahjongg Solitaire', 3770, 'Relax and unwind with Mahjongg Solitaire! Match pairs of mahjongg tiles to clear the board and complete each level. With beautiful designs and satisfying puzzles, it&amp;rsquo;s the perfect game for a peaceful challenge!', 'Point and Click', 'English'),
('Plants vs Zombies Coloring', 3771, 'Plants vs. Zombies Coloring Game is a creative and relaxing game that lets players bring their favorite plants and zombies to life with vibrant colors. Dive into the world of Plants vs. Zombies and unleash your artistic talent by coloring iconic characters, scenes, and battles from the popular series. Choose your favorite plants, zombies, or scenes and add your personal touch by coloring them with a wide range of colors and tools. Save your masterpiece and share it with friends!', 'Mouse', 'English'),
('Mecha Shoot Pixel Rpg', 3772, 'Enter the world of Mecha Shoot Pixel RPG. This is an exciting mix of shooting, RPG, and intense battle action. Control a powerful mecha in a pixelated style. Engage in nervous shooting combat against waves of monsters. You will control your direction and keep shooting at the enemy. Avoid their attacks and find the time to defeat them.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pendulum Goal   Casual Physics', 3773, 'Pendulum Goal is an interactive game that allows players to explore the physical behavior of pendulums on different planets. The objective is to dodge swinging pendulums that move according to the gravity of each stage (Earth, Moon, and Jupiter). Besides being a fun experience, the game also teaches physics concepts, such as the relationship between a pendulum&amp;rsquo;s period and length based on the gravity of each environment.', 'How to Play Objective Avoid the pendulums while trying to score goals Controls The game is controlled with a single button to kick the ball', 'English'),
('Squid Game X Sprunki Tetris', 3774, 'Squid Game X Sprunki Tetris in a tetris match, enjoy!', 'INSTRUCTIONS MOVE - ARROW KEYS Z X - ROTATE LEFT RIGHT SPACE - DROP', 'English'),
('Newtons Fruit Fusion', 3775, 'Newtons Fruit Fusion is a fun and challenging game where you drop fruits onto the screen. Match similar fruits to create bigger ones. Plan your moves carefully, as the game gets harder with each level. Can you create the greatest fruit? Test your strategy and enjoy this exciting merging puzzle game!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to drop fruits', 'English'),
('Toy Game For Kids', 3776, 'This is a collection of games for toddlers. Our games offer a variety of game modes including spinner, bubble blower, and surprise egg. They are anti-stress and relaxing games and toy gadgets designed to hone kids attention and motor skills. You can also press bubbles, play with crocodile toys, and more.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Flex Escape', 3777, 'Flex Escape 3D is a fun game where you stretch and flex to avoid obstacles. Instead of running, you stay on a mat and use your flexibility to dodge furniture and appliances thrown at you. By moving left or right with simple controls, you can navigate through the challenges. Collecting gems helps unlock new objects, making the game even more exciting. The goal is to make it to the end without hitting any obstacles while staying focused and flexible.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
