('Squid Game Sprunki Hide', 3779, 'Squid game and sprunki hiding something. Reveal the fishy squid scattered around before time run out!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Noobik Parkour in a Cave!', 3780, 'The game has 10 hardcore levels! To complete the level, you need to get to the finish line, overcoming various obstacles, dodging various traps on your way!', 'Mobile devices Touch joystick on the left side of the screen - Move Right side of the screen - Rotate the camera Button in the lower right corner - Jump Computers WASD - Move Space - Jump Escape - Pause menu Mouse movement - Rotate the camera', 'English'),
('Fruit Match: Juicy Puzzle', 3781, 'Enjoy a juicy adventure with Fruit Match, a fun and colorful puzzle game! Match and collect delicious fruits to clear levels and unlock bonuses. With vibrant graphics and engaging gameplay, this game is perfect for kids and families looking for casual fun. Test your matching skills and enjoy endless fruity challenges!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Fire Truck Rescue Driving', 3782, 'Fire Truck Rescue Driving is an exciting driving game that allows you to become a firefighter.Driving the fire engine quickly to the scene of the fire for emergency rescue. The fire scenes and fast driving in the game make you feel a sense of urgency to put out the fire. You must drive the fire engine quickly and carefully to avoid hitting other vehicles.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Master', 3783, 'Sprunki Master is an exciting Stickman Music game inspired by the popular music-mixing game Incredibox. It builds on the original games creative foundation with fresh soundscapes, visuals, and interactive elements. Created by VodoGame, Sprunki Master introduces new characters, beats, rhythms, and melodies, offering music lovers and gamers a vibrant platform to explore their creativity.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box', 3784, 'Dive into a rhythm-filled horror adventure! Join the scary yet fun-filled musical journey in Sprunki Music Scary Beat Box. Explore four unique modes: Rhythm, Monster, Joker and Beat, each offering a completely different musical challenge and fun! Each mode requires you to drag the character around and feel different music or movements. Casual gameplay is perfect for all ages.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Popdify', 3785, 'Popdify is a fast-paced skill game where precision is key! Hold to release popcorn and aim to fill the cup perfectly&amp;mdash;drop even one kernel, and it&amp;rsquo;s game over. With simple controls, challenging gameplay, and endless fun, can you master the art of perfect popping?', 'Hold to release popcorn into the cup but be precise mdash drop even one kernel and its game over', 'English'),
('Climb Up', 3786, 'In this challenging adventure, youll embark on a perilous ascent up a massive, treacherous mountain. Navigate slippery surfaces and unpredictable obstacles as you make your way towards the summit, where eternal glory and a rewarding gift await. Will you be able to overcome the many hurdles and reach the top, or will the climb prove too daunting? Your determination and skill will be tested as you brave the unknowns of this grueling climb.', 'Use JoySticks', 'English'),
('Idle Explorers', 3787, '**Idle Explorers** is an engaging idle adventure game where you lead a team of explorers on exciting journeys to discover hidden treasures and mysterious artifacts. Upgrade your explorers, unlock new biomes, and collect rewards even while offline. Strategically manage your crew and expand your empire to become the ultimate adventurer!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
