('Silent Asylum 2', 3788, 'Silent Asylum 2 features eerie atmosphere of a foggy town where your mission is to shoot scary monsters using different weapons and find the exit on each level in order to progress with your adventure.', 'WASD - Move LMB - Shoot RMB - Aim Flashlight Space - Jump R - Reload G - Grenade F - Use C - Crouch Shift - Run', 'English'),
