('Squid Clicker Game 2', 3798, 'In Squid Clicker Game 2, you have 60 seconds to make as many clicks as possible and rack up an impressive score. The faster you click, the more loot you uncover, and the stakes get higher with every second! Look out for special time bonuses that can extend your run and give you more chances to boost your score. Can you outpace your own speed and become the ultimate clicker champion? It&amp;rsquo;s an exciting, fast-paced game designed to challenge your reflexes and push your limits. How many clicks can you make before time runs out? Prove youre the best!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Incredibox Party Frozen Sprunki Beat', 3799, 'Get ready to dive into a unique mix of music, horror, and beats in the Incredibox Party Frozen Sprunki Beat! This game lets you create eerie yet rhythmic melodies by combining spooky sounds with chilling visual effects.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('RealFX Driving Simulator', 3800, 'RealFX Driving Simulator a real simulator. When driving meet reality, here its the result', 'WASD to move', 'English'),
('Demolition Derby Car 3d', 3801, 'Play the exciting car derby racing game with unique graphics and smooth controls. The 2025 car derby demolition game is now in your hands to drive the car fastly.', 'Play with keyboard arrow keys', 'English'),
('Ice is coming', 3802, 'Move the ice block to the designated position by touching it, and eliminate the line when it is completed. See who can hold on for the longest time', 'Move the ice cube to the designated position by touching it', 'English'),
('Mecha Storm Robot Battle', 3803, 'Get ready for the nervous action of Mecha Storm: Robot Battle. This game puts you in the future technology world and becomes a robot warrior. Fight with other robot warriors on the battlefield!Here, you need to strategically upgrade and modify your Mecha to defeat wave after wave of enemies!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Milky Way', 3804, 'Embark on an interstellar adventure with Milky Way, a fast-paced arcade game set in the mysterious expanses of outer space. Navigate through a captivating cosmic environment, dodging obstacles and avoiding intergalactic dangers.', 'Objective Your goal is to dash through the cosmic terrain avoiding obstacles and collecting points Controls Tap the screen to make your character jump and dodge incoming obstacles Strategy Stay focused and time your jumps perfectly to avoid falling', 'English'),
('New Years Balls 2048 in 3D', 3805, 'A game with a New Years atmosphere! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone, where balls fall and connect if they have the same color! Connect as many balls as possible to get the biggest one, collect points! Become the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect the balls but over time there will be more and more of them Once you connect the biggest ball in this game it will disappear and give you the most points', 'English'),
